### Variables (optional)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5064
@contentType = application/json
@productRef = 3

### Get all products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Product

### Get specific product
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Product/{{productRef}}

### Create new product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Product
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Test Product",
  "price": 79.99
}

### Update product
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/Product/{{productRef}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": 4,
  "name": "Updated Product",
  "price": 39.99
}

### Delete product
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/Product/{{productRef}}